Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,our class has decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...to hold a fortune-telling parlor for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone, please decide on the method of fortune-telling you will be doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...before our next homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was thinking about doing a cheerleading routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheerleading?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For the opening ceremony we talked about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be the best performance for bringing the festival to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does sound pretty crazy and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the talk of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By we, do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we're a part of it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and was told there has to be a properly structured outline, including the performers' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What about you, Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be physically tough on Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much trouble, I was thinking maybe I could give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more than welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I might just hold everyone else back,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to give a try this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka's willing to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if everyone's doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I have such good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortune-telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even do any sort of fortune-telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, weren't you the one who proposed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For a culture festival, fortune-telling can be pretty much whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what's your class doing, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We just decided to be simple and do a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't come up with any other interesting ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought it suited you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The devil's mad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were gonna say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty-chan said she wanted to do a cheerleading routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking, "Maybe I'll give it a try, too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been absent a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've never had the chance to accomplish something with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been feeling a lot better these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and what Patty-chan wants to do right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably not all that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still think it's going to be pretty tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,since we don't have enough people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty-chan was wondering if you would join us, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really athletic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so if people like you and Minami-chan are there with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll be able to hang in there until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you seem to be really serious about this, and because Patty's also asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Patty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard the story and was thinking about what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pin Pon Pan Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a certain ticket in my other hand right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what do you think the ticket is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gekisou was pretty moé moé, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you want to exchange a hot handshake with Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, handshake session!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Must meet Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Konata,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you were trying to say something earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make some nice memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the age of cheerleading girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty wanted to do a cheerleading routine during the culture festival's opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That does fit her image.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why the both of you are also on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are there any other people in your class who might be interested, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just go on ahead without our permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think I'm suited for that kind of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But we probably won't get another chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We know everyone on the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a festival, so it'll be more fun if we go crazy with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, you're so easily convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to prepare for my own class projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make some memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...with my best friends during our last culture festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You always seem to pull the friendship card when there are ulterior motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clearly obvious you're putting on an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan is really enthusiastic about this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her she shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was really earnest about wanting to accomplish something with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're having trouble getting enough people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I would ask you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was a little too pushy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would hate to make you guys do something you really didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just ask someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, my class can just replace me with someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are no replacements for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, you're so cute after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cheerleading is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident that I can do a good job...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now we're just trying to fill the gaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in terms of volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you joined us, it would help a great deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much Boin{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that testing is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be focusing on preparations for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't slack off too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They could at least cut down on the testing when we have school events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with the cheerleading thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Before exams started,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"The plan was approved,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard anything since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't start practicing soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it might already be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll go ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't worked out the choreography yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't worked out the choreography yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do then!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also taking me a while to pick the song...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard finding something on Hare Hare's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were troubled about it, you should have talked it over with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that came up with the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so you need to be more responsible about the scheduling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand these hard Japanese words!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying after speaking it so fluently up until now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At least decide on some of the choreography today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll work out the awkward spots as we practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something you can't figure out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ask someone you're comfortable talking to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki and I will handle the practice scheduling and reserve a suitable location to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the hardest one to get on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you seem the most passionate about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be doing tarot readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, can you think of something that even I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How about one that involves reading shapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...means that your love fortune is looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You made that up just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect us to learn all that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a matter of good or bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks fairly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll just have to simplify some of the harder parts as we go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we overcome these obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a great sense of accomplishment awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of gum-tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a run to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, grab some sharpies while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And some X-Acto replacement blades, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cardboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard some stuff I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's that much stuff that needs to be bought,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,stop messing around and go buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we calling the yakisoba again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fragrant Breath of Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Fallen Drop of Sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the okonomiyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no idea what's on this menu unless you ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese culture is so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Though this project seems to be a bit slanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A Zuka Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a place where you can enjoy shows in the spirit of Zuka with the comforts of a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With girls in graceful dresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and beautiful male attire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...as your designated waitresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Male...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan and Minami-chan are the leads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A dazzling, ever-evolving world of beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When was this decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous about the cheerleading,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but is this going to be okay, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're perfectly in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that would be considered sadistic on Miyuki-san's part,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or masochistic on Minami-chan's part?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Takara-senpai's dynamic dance moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...can put quite the pressure on Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that and just practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The cheerleading costumes are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's slightly embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But these kind of costumes are what make the viewers happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, they were chosen by a person who enjoys watching this sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the one you mentioned last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The dreaded older Tamura brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look forward to some great Zuka costumes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you guys are going to do a cheerleading routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take pictures!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Within reasonable limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't had a successful run-through yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lend you some of my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get too much of Nee-san's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we'll be too energetic and tire ourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in quite a bind right now considering how we don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we did for ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We had, what you would call,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a "manga café" in today's terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All the boys in our class...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...brought their manga collection to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were ahead of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it may seem normal to bring manga to school, nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,back in my day, they were pretty strict about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They only let us do it because of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, people do bring it to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like it's officially approved...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fortune-telling parlor, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to give me a good fortune when I come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But then that wouldn't be fortune-telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,how was it back in your day, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Each class or club would have their own activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of classes did stuff like haunted houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or okonomiyaki shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty standard stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather strange how...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...things haven't changed much over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was something like, "An inquiry regarding cultural objects such as Paulownia dressers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ever used as an activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be so boring, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we'll be able to put on an exciting performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're not finished yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's make sure we keep it up until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's times like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's nice to have Hiiragi here to take command!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be the only one left without memories with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that today is just a rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only for students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be open to the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...until tomorrow for people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to check before coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Akira-chan would be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of a train fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we still had that money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we could have bought ourselves a hamburger steak or something fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's coming together pretty nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're walking around dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, we can advertise ourselves better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan's get-up is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Always gotta start with appearances, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll read lots of fortunes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In 5 minutes and 15 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you will buy some soft-serve ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At 5 minutes and 28 seconds, you will drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At 7 minutes and 6 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you will hit your head on a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's foretelling, not fortune-telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Too exact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But we aren't going to lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut it pretty close,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I finished just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really embarrassing to walk around in this costume, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogami Akira is about to go on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's just a rehearsal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so just take it easy out there while we run some check-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the culture festival's Executive Committee Chairman Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to leave the rest up to Shiraishi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so just let him know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just gone to the demon council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something... wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just doing some planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and got a little too excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,since you are an appreciated guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll treat you accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to have you do a mic check for Misoji Misaki during Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to say whatever you want after the song on stage tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do a good job then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,please get up on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Shiraishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to see Akira, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have a great time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Longing to be in the arms of the person she loves,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when will such a day come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As she wanders endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,guided by his words from that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll go anywhere in order to find a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is her song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogami Akira-san with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...Misoji Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me sing my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it was only a mic test today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't understand these difficult Japanese words!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last dress-rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This was just an idea I had on a whim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but having the opportunity to do something with all of my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of worrying about success or failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everyone should just enjoy themselves out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We were practicing our cheerleading routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could buy some drinks for you kids for trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special occasion, so it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In return,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,promise me you'll make the first event at the culture festival tomorrow a total blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure how to describe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels kinda strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm also feeling a little melancholic myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the most enjoyable part of a festival is when you're preparing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably never stay at school this late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way, it does feel a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tamura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your face is really strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,my stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, I bet you're frozen stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your usual cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Being nervous helps you focus more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm so nervous I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Test. Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we will commence the Outou Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The first performance today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...was submitted by a foreign student, Patricia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A cheerleading routine performed by her group of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I present to you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mirakuru Mikurun run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would please turn off your cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble up until the very end, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I loosened up so much I almost fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that guy so lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that trouble just tends to follow certain people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's appropriate for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How we can ever be completely serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get to our momentum back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Motteke! Sailor-fuku!
